---
title: Beef Rump & Honey-Roasted Veggie Freekeh with Almonds & Yoghurt
description: Nan’s special seasoning is full of flavour, thanks to paprika, pepper, onion and garlic, and when used as a coating it makes this tender beef rump simply heavenly! Add a medley of veggies, crunchy flaked almonds and a dollop of rich and tangy garlic yoghurt for satisfaction, guaranteed!
